OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVarying amounts of cloud, this
OL,6,Fperhaps thick enough to produce a very
OL,7,Fisolated light shower. Still bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells will occur, and most
OL,9,Fplaces will be dry and very warm with
OL,10,Flight winds, these onshore along the
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with often large amounts
OL,14,Fof cloud, but also clear spells will
OL,15,Foccur, which may allow patchy mist or
OL,16,Ffog to form in rural areas later
OL,17,Ftonight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
